pettiness.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304\u00a020781 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32089,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/allah-supports-rifq\/","url_meta":{"origin":36562,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rifq: Allah supports kindness, gentleness and loves it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty loves gentleness and is pleased with it. He lends support for in a way he does not support harshness.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 7477 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32272,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/abu-dharr-loves-allah-rasul\/","url_meta":{"origin":36562,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Abu Dharr loves Allah and His Messenger","author":"Abu Amina Eli